Flights from JFK Airport

Source: R/data.R
flights_jfk.Rd

A modified subset of flights.

flights_jfk

Format

A tibble with 12,367 rows and 10 columns:

year

year of arrival, 2012-2013

date

scheduled date of arrival

hour

hour of scheduled arrival, 9 AM to 9 PM

carrier

airline carrier, American Airlines (AA), Jet Blue (B6), and Delta (DL)

dest

destination, Las Vegas (LAS), Los Angeles (LAX), and San Francisco (SFO)

tailnum

tail number of plane

distance

distance from origin to destination

air_time

time in air from origin to destination

dep_delay

departure delay (minutes)

arr_delay

arrival delay (minutes)

temp

temperature (F)

dewp

dewpoint (F)

humid

relative humidity

wind_dir

wind direction (degrees)

wind_speed

wind speed (mph)

precip

precipitaton (inches)

pressure

sea level pressure (millibars)

visib

visibility (miles)
